    - Put this file at the project root and adjust the value for your environment.




/* ___________________________________________________________________________________
/* ___________________________ NAMING STANDARDS ______________________________________

    Names and codification used in this project. Langage used must be English. :
   
    HTML:
        - Classes, attributs (alts, titles, aria-labels), Ids and input names : .kebab-case
        - Quotes : "double quotes"
    
    CSS:
        - Vars : var(--camelCase).
        - Use a space after the colon in property declarations.
        - Use a semicolon after each property declaration.
        - Use a space between selectors and the opening brace.
        - Use a new line for each selector and declaration.
    
    JavaScript:
        - Var, let, functions = let camelCase.
        - Constants = const UPPERCASE_SNAKE_CASE.
        - Class and constructor names : PascalCase.
        - Quotes : 'single quotes'.
        - Prioritise let over var for variable declarations.
        - Prioritise arrow functions instead of function expressions where possible.
        - Use meaningful variable and function names.
    
    PHP:
        - Variables : $camelCase.
        - Constants : define('UPPERCASE_SNAKE_CASE', 'value').
        - Functions : function camelCase().
        - Classes : class PascalCase.
        - Quotes : 'single quotes'.
        - Use meaningful variable and function names.
    


/* ___________________________________________________________________________________
/* ___________________________ CSS CODE STANDARDS ______________________________________

    Please use and keep in mind the CSS Code Standard below for this project :

    /* ______________________________________ ELEMENTS ______________________________________ : *

    /* Box Model */
    /* Positioning and Layout */
    /* Typography */
    /* Borders, Effects and Backgrounds */
    /* Others */

    /* ______________________________________ EXAMPLE ______________________________________ : *

    /* MY FILE */
    /*________ MY ELEMENTS, MY ELEMENTS HOVER ________*/
    .my-element {
        /* Box Model*/
        width: 200px;
        height: 100px;
        margin: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        
        /* Positioning and Layout */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        position: relative;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 1;

        /* Typography */
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #333;

        /* Borders, Effects and Backgrounds */
        border: 2px solid #333;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        background-image: url('image.jpg');
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        
        /* Others */
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
  